Class AppointmentOutcomeRecordContainer

Object
RecordContainer
AppointmentOutcomeRecordContainer
All Implemented Interfaces:
Container
public class AppointmentOutcomeRecordContainer extends RecordContainer
Container class for managing appointment outcome records. Provides functionalities for loading, adding, and exporting appointment outcomes.
